4.3 Scarcity Timer
Implementation:
javascript// Start 10-minute countdown when item added to cart
const CART_TIMER_DURATION = 10 * 60 * 1000; // 10 minutes

const CartTimer = () => {
  const [timeRemaining, setTimeRemaining] = useState(CART_TIMER_DURATION);
  
  useEffect(() => {
    const timer = setInterval(() => {
      setTimeRemaining(prev => {
        if (prev <= 0) {
          // Show urgency message
          return 0;
        }
        return prev - 1000;
      });
    }, 1000);
    
    return () => clearInterval(timer);
  }, []);
  
  return (
    <div className="cart-timer">
      <Icon name="clock" />
      <span>Seu carrinho expira em: {formatTime(timeRemaining)}</span>
      <ProgressBar percentage={(timeRemaining / CART_TIMER_DURATION) * 100} />
    </div>
  );
};
Visual Design:

Red #CF111A color for urgency
Clock icon
Progress bar showing time remaining
Message: "Complete sua compra em [MM:SS] para garantir disponibilidade"

4.4 Smart Product Recommendations
Recommendation Logic:
javascriptconst getCartRecommendations = (cartItems) => {
  // Logic 1: Frequently Bought Together
  const productIds = cartItems.map(item => item.product.id);
  const fbtProducts = await fetchFrequentlyBoughtTogether(productIds);
  
  // Logic 2: Complementary Products
  const categories = cartItems.map(item => item.product.product_type);
  const complementary = await fetchComplementaryProducts(categories);
  
  // Logic 3: Same Age Range
  const ageRanges = cartItems.flatMap(item => item.product.tags.filter(tag => tag.includes('age-')));
  const sameAge = await fetchProductsByAgeTags(ageRanges);
  
  // Combine and deduplicate
  const recommendations = [...new Set([...fbtProducts, ...complementary, ...sameAge])]
    .filter(product => !productIds.includes(product.id))
    .slice(0, 4); // Limit to 4 recommendations
  
  return recommendations;
};
Display:

Section title: "Complete sua Experi√™ncia"
Horizontal scrollable carousel (4 products visible)
Mini product cards: image, title, price, "+Adicionar" button
Below cart items, above subtotal

