5. POP-UP SYSTEM
5.1 Email & WhatsApp Collection Pop-up
Trigger Logic:
javascriptconst EmailPopupManager = {
  COOKIE_NAME: 'brinqueteando_email_popup',
  MAX_VIEWS: 2,
  COOLDOWN_DAYS: 10,
  
  shouldShow: () => {
    const cookie = getCookie(COOKIE_NAME);
    if (!cookie) return true;
    
    const { views, lastShown, subscribed } = JSON.parse(cookie);
    
    if (subscribed) return false;
    
    const daysSinceLastShown = (Date.now() - lastShown) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24);
    
    if (views >= MAX_VIEWS && daysSinceLastShown < COOLDOWN_DAYS) {
      return false;
    }
    
    if (daysSinceLastShown >= COOLDOWN_DAYS) {
      // Reset counter after cooldown
      return true;
    }
    
    return views < MAX_VIEWS;
  },
  
  recordView: () => {
    const cookie = getCookie(COOKIE_NAME);
    let data = cookie ? JSON.parse(cookie) : { views: 0, lastShown: Date.now(), subscribed: false };
    
    data.views += 1;
    data.lastShown = Date.now();
    
    setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, JSON.stringify(data), 365); // 1 year expiry
  },
  
  recordSubscription: () => {
    const data = { views: MAX_VIEWS, lastShown: Date.now(), subscribed: true };
    setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, JSON.stringify(data), 365);
  }
};
Display Timing:

Shows after 15 seconds on site (first visit)
OR after scrolling 50% down the page
Checks shouldShow() before displaying

Design:

Modal overlay (semi-transparent backdrop)
Pop-up box: Light Blue #8ECAE7 background
Puzzle piece decorative elements
Close button (X, top-right)

Content:

Headline: "Junte-se √† Comunidade BrinqueTEAndo! üß©"
Subheadline: "Receba dicas exclusivas, novidades e promo√ß√µes especiais"
Form fields:

Nome (text input)
Email (email input, required)
WhatsApp (tel input with BR format mask, required)


Checkbox: "Aceito receber comunica√ß√µes" (required)
CTA button: "CADASTRAR" (Dark Blue #21388D)
Privacy link: "Pol√≠tica de Privacidade"

Post-Submission:

Success message: "Obrigado! Voc√™ est√° cadastrado üéâ"
Auto-close after 3 seconds
Call recordSubscription() to prevent future displays

5.2 Exit Intent Pop-up (Discount)
Trigger Logic:
javascriptconst ExitPopupManager = {
  COOKIE_NAME: 'brinqueteando_exit_popup',
  MAX_VIEWS: 2,
  COOLDOWN_DAYS: 10,
  
  shouldShow: () => {
    // Same logic as EmailPopupManager
    const cookie = getCookie(COOKIE_NAME);
    if (!cookie) return true;
    
    const { views, lastShown, converted } = JSON.parse(cookie);
    
    if (converted) return false;
    
    const daysSinceLastShown = (Date.now() - lastShown) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24);
    
    if (views >= MAX_VIEWS && daysSinceLastShown < COOLDOWN_DAYS) {
      return false;
    }
    
    if (daysSinceLastShown >= COOLDOWN_DAYS) {
      return true;
    }
    
    return views < MAX_VIEWS;
  },
  
  recordView: () => {
    const cookie = getCookie(COOKIE_NAME);
    let data = cookie ? JSON.parse(cookie) : { views: 0, lastShown: Date.now(), converted: false };
    
    data.views += 1;
    data.lastShown = Date.now();
    
    setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, JSON.stringify(data), 365);
  },
  
  recordConversion: () => {
    const data = { views: MAX_VIEWS, lastShown: Date.now(), converted: true };
    setCookie(COOKIE_NAME, JSON.stringify(data), 365);
  }
};
Exit Intent Detection:
javascriptdocument.addEventListener('mouseout', (e) => {
  if (e.clientY <= 0 && ExitPopupManager.shouldShow()) {
    showExitPopup();
    ExitPopupManager.recordView();
  }
});

// Mobile: detect back button or scroll to top aggressively
let lastScrollTop = 0;
window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
  const scrollTop = window.pageYOffset || document.documentElement.scrollTop;
  if (scrollTop < lastScrollTop && scrollTop < 50 && ExitPopupManager.shouldShow()) {
    showExitPopup();
    ExitPopupManager.recordView();
  }
  lastScrollTop = scrollTop;
}, false);
Design:

Modal overlay (darker, more prominent)
Pop-up box: Red #CF111A accent with Light Blue #8ECAE7 background
Dragon mascot illustration
Close button (X, top-right)

Content:

Headline: "ESPERE! N√£o V√° Embora Ainda! üêâ"
Subheadline: "Ganhe at√© 20% de desconto na sua primeira compra"
Discount code display: Large, prominent code
Discount tiers:

10% OFF: Compras acima de R$ 100 - C√≥digo: PRIMEIRA10
15% OFF: Compras acima de R$ 200 - C√≥digo: PRIMEIRA15
20% OFF: Compras acima de R$ 300 - C√≥digo: PRIMEIRA20


Expiry statement: "V√°lido por 24 horas"
CTA button: "USAR MEU DESCONTO" (applies code to cart, closes popup)
Secondary link: "N√£o, obrigado" (closes popup)

Post-Use:

If user clicks CTA, call recordConversion() to prevent future displays
Apply discount code to cart automatically
Show confirmation toast: "Desconto aplicado! üéâ"


