13.2 Urgency & Scarcity Tactics
Ethical Implementation:

Low stock indicators (when genuinely low)
Limited-time offers (real deadlines)
Cart timer (as specified)
"X people viewing this" (if tracking implemented)
Seasonal collections
No fake scarcity - build real trust

13.3 Social Proof
