17. RISK MITIGATION
17.1 Technical Risks
Risk: Hydrogen framework learning curve
Mitigation: Allocate time for team training, use Shopify documentation, consider Shopify partners for consultation
Risk: Performance issues with large product catalogs
Mitigation: Implement lazy loading, optimize images, use CDN, monitor Core Web Vitals
Risk: Pop-up blocking by browsers
Mitigation: Ensure pop-ups comply with browser standards, test across browsers, provide alternative signup paths
17.2 Business Risks
Risk: Low initial traffic
Mitigation: Invest in SEO from launch, consider paid ads for quick wins, leverage social media, partner with local organizations
Risk: High cart abandonment
Mitigation: Optimize checkout flow, offer multiple payment methods, implement retargeting emails, reduce shipping costs
Risk: Competition from established stores
Mitigation: Focus on niche positioning (ADHD/Autism specific), excellent customer service, educational content, community building

